## Troubleshooting

| Error | Solution |
|-------|----------|
| "Cannot find module '.prisma/client'" | `npx prisma generate` |
| "Table doesn't exist" | `npx prisma migrate dev --name "sync"` |
| "Database locked" | Restart dev server |
| Types don't match | `npx prisma generate` |
| "Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'findMany')" | Add model to ULID extension in `lib/utils/ulid.ts`, then `npx prisma generate` and restart |
